#

Roasted Root Vegetable Medley with Citrus Vinaigrette

$15
180 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Tags:

VeganHealthySeasonal

Description

A vibrant medley of roasted carrots, parsnips, and sweet potatoes drizzled with a zesty citrus vinaigrette, perfect as a side or light main dish.

Ingredients

  • Carrots: 2 cups, peeled and chopped
  • Parsnips: 2 cups, peeled and chopped
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 cups, peeled and chopped
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Salt: 1 teaspoon
  • Black Pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Fresh Orange Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh Lemon Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Honey (or Agave Syrup for vegan): 1 tablespoon
  • Mustard (Dijon or Whole Grain): 1 teaspoon
  • Chopped Fresh Herbs (Parsley or Thyme): 1/4 cup
